<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Account Verification Revoked | RecruitWay</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12 0%, #e67e22 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .notice-card {
            background-color: #fff8f0;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
        }

        .action-card {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #3498db;
        }

        .company-info {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }

        a {
            color: #3498db;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Verification Revoked</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello <strong>
                    <%= email %>
                </strong>,</p>

            <div class="notice-card">
                <p>We regret to inform you that your RecruitWay account verification has been revoked effective
                    immediately.</p>
                <p>This action was taken due to one of the following reasons:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Violation of our Terms of Service</li>
                    <li>Suspicious account activity</li>
                    <li>Administrative review decision</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="action-card">
                <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
                <p>If you believe this action was taken in error, you may appeal this decision by contacting our support
                    team at <a href="mailto:support@recruitway.com">support@recruitway.com</a> within 14 days.</p>
                <p>Please include any relevant information that may help us review your case.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="signature">
                <p>Thank you for your understanding,<br>
                    <strong>RecruitWay Trust & Safety Team</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/recruitway">LinkedIn</a> |
                <a href="https://twitter.com/recruitway">Twitter</a> |
                <a href="https://facebook.com/recruitway">Facebook</a>
            </div>
            <div class="company-info">
                <p>
                    RecruitWay Inc.<br>
                    123 Business Avenue, Suite 100<br>
                    San Francisco, CA 94107
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>